nba <- read_csv("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/brendanrbrown/brendanrbrown.github.io/master/nba-teams-2017.csv") %>%
  select(-games_played, -minutes)

nba <- select(nba, -team)

m <- prcomp(nba, scale. =  TRUE)

pcs <- as.data.frame(m$rotation)

ggplot(pcs, aes(x = PC2, y = PC3)) + geom_point(color = "Red") + ggtitle("PC2 by PC3")

ggplot(pcs, aes(x = PC2, y = PC3, label = rownames(m$rotation))) + 
  geom_point(colour = "purple3") + geom_label(size = 5) + theme_minimal() + 
  xlim(-.45, .4) + ylim(-.3, .45)
## Warning: Removed 2 rows containing missing values (geom_point).
## Warning: Removed 2 rows containing missing values (geom_label).

m2 <- kmeans(m$x[, c(2,3)], 4)

score <- as_tibble(m$x)

score %>% mutate(cluster = factor(m2$cluster)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(PC2, PC3, color = cluster, label = team)) + geom_label(size = 4) +
  theme_bw() + scale_color_brewer(type = "qual", palette = "Set1") + xlim(-7, 7)
